193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #The 6502 interrupt vectors are:
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #- IRQ/BRK: `FFFE-FFFF` (maskable interrupt)
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #- NMI: `FFFA-FFFB` (non-maskable interrupt)
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #- RESET: `FFFC-FFFD` (reset vector)
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #Each vector is 16-bit (2 bytes, little-endian), holding the address where execution jumps when that
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #interrupt occurs.
193aac4a [claude-haiku-4-5] #
