193ab876 [simon@midnightblue] can reset be disabled?
193ab8b6 [deepseek-chat] #No. RESET cannot be disabled on the 6502. It's a hardware-level input that always triggers
193ab8b6 [deepseek-chat] #a full processor reset when asserted (held low). There's no software control or status flag to mask
