193ad551 [grok-4.20-0309] #
193ad551 [grok-4.20-0309] #Summary – RESET is available on 3 external connectors:
193ad551 [grok-4.20-0309] #
193ad551 [grok-4.20-0309] #1. User Port (the big 44-pin edge connector on the left) → Pin 1
