1a7b5b21 [gemini-3.1-pro] #TV is turned on, it takes extra time to find the sync timing once the active lines resume.
1a7b5b21 [gemini-3.1-pro] #
1a7b5b21 [gemini-3.1-pro] #To improve the signal lock, you will need to maintain horizontal sync pulses throughout the
1a7b5b21 [gemini-3.1-pro] #blanking lines, or implement the proper PAL broad sync pulses.
